It’s makeover 🛠 week, but it’s also the back-to-school sale! Everything in my TpT store is 25% off using code BTS21.

So if you’ve been eyeing one of my resources, now is your chance to grab it!

node.text:
💪🏼🛠 It’s MaKeOvEr time!!! Picked up the Uhaul today and went all around Columbus picking up furniture. Excited to transform another space with my team!

Also, lots of new followers lately. Welcome to my little corner of the internet! This is my wife— she’s 8 months pregnant and a total rockstar. I share a lot about her and if that’s not something you can support, feel free to unfollow!

For the rest of you incredible humans who have so openly rooted for us along the way, we appreciate you! Pumped to share another makeover with you!

#classroommakeover #classroomdecor #classroomdesign #classroomideas #classroomorganization #teachersfollowteachers #iteachtoo #teachersofig #teachersofinsta #teachersofinstagram

node.text:
📓✏️ Exit tickets were my go-to for classroom management, routine and reflection when I was in the classroom, so I designed an exit ticket journal with daily exit ticket prompts!

Click the link in my bio to see if this resource works for you and your students!

Details:
- Printer friendly
- Digital included
- Any subject area
- Focuses on reflection + student understanding
- Daily prompts for the entire year
- No prep for you

https://www.teacherspayteachers.com/Product/Exit-Ticket-Journal-for-ANY-Subject-275-Exit-Ticket-Prompts-for-Grades-5-12-3420552

#exitticket #classroommanagement #classroomroutine #iteachtoo #iteachela #elateacher #iteach678 #middleschoolteacher #highschoolteacher #upperelementary #iteach5th #iteach6th #iteach7th #iteach8th

node.text:
🌊 Did you know that @elkay_usa has already saved more than 40 BILLION plastic bottles from polluting our earth and oceans?! 💦 That is HUGE. You can be part of the solution, too. #elkaypartner

Their ezH2O system is so simple to use and is an essential for creating safe drinking water for all students.

Learn more about how YOU can fundraise and get one installed in your school using the link in my bio.

https://www.elkay.com/us/en/drinking-water/collections/ez-wish-kit.html

#savetheocean #reduceplastic #teachersofinstagram #teachersofig #teachersofinsta #iteachtoo

node.text:
Wednesday is the LAST DAY to purchase your ticket for the virtual Classroom Environment and Design Conference!!!

This is your opportunity to learn about all things classroom environment, design, atmosphere, and decor.

When you purchase, you’ll have immediate access AND lifetime access to all of the sessions, 24+ free bonus resources, and a chance to win a classroom makeover!

Use the link in my bio to register.

https://thesuperheroteacher.com/classroom-design-environment-conference-2021

#classroomdesign #classroomdecor #classroomtips #iteachtoo #teachersofig #teachersofinstagram
